- cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely category as the paper deals with logical characterization of program properties and reductions to HFL model checking. 
- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is also likely as the paper discusses verification of higher-order functional programs. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is relevant as the paper deals with model checking of temporal properties. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is possible as the paper discusses automated verification of software programs. 
- cs.LG (Machine Learning) is less likely but still possible as the paper mentions linear-time temporal properties, which could be related to machine learning algorithms.
